# Task Management

Canonical rule lives in `haderach-tasks/.cursor/rules/todo-conventions.mdc`.
Read that file for the full policy.

**Local defaults:** When creating a task from this repo, write it to
`../haderach-tasks/tasks/` and set `group: vendors` and `phase: vendors`.
When reading tasks for this repo, prefer items with `group: vendors`.
